Mirror on SourceForge

To get the latest development sources, first install subversion client and run one of the following commands:

# stable branch for Qt6 (bug fixes only)

svn checkout http://svn.code.sf.net/p/qmmp-dev/code/branches/qmmp-2.1/ qmmp-2.1

# development branch for Qt6

svn checkout http://svn.code.sf.net/p/qmmp-dev/code/trunk/qmmp/ qmmp-2.2

# stable branch for Qt5 (bug fixes only)

svn checkout http://svn.code.sf.net/p/qmmp-dev/code/branches/qmmp-1.6/ qmmp-1.6

# stable branch for Qt4 (bug fixes only)

svn checkout http://svn.code.sf.net/p/qmmp-dev/code/branches/qmmp-0.12/ qmmp-0.12
